+// DOS-PORT (patch 0087, Phase 9 wave 20 Lever A): per-phase flip()
+// timing brackets opt-in. Strict "1" match, default OFF (instrumentation
+// has its own cost — 5 SDL_GetTicksNS calls per flip + per-100-flip
